	<text>
		<body>
			<p>From Consul <persName ref="#ehri_dr_yukio_toyohara">Toyohara Yukio</persName> (<placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2035836/manzhouli.html">Manchouli</placeName>)</p>
			<p>To: Japanese Ambassador to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/maps/wikipedia_43.8833_125.3167.html">Manchukuo</placeName>
				<persName ref="#ehri_dr_umezu_yoshijirō"> Umetsu Yoshijirō</persName></p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> are being seriously <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-642" type="subject">persecuted</term> by the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1159" type="subject">Nazi regime</term>. It is not an exaggeration to say
				that those fellow [<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>] living in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">Germany</placeName> are suffering from tremendous hardship.
				This time when they left Germany their <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-585" type="subject">properties
					were confiscated</term> and they were not allowed to bring funds or clothing….</p>
		</body>
